                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
                            <span class="zh">分岔点：1843-1845年，赫德森的财务操作</span>
                            <span class="en">Fork: 1843-1845, Hudson's Financial Operations</span>
                        </p>
