                            <span class="zh"><strong>赫德森用新股东的钱付老股东的股息。</strong>他将资本性支出计入运营成本，通过关联公司之间的资金转移隐匿亏损。这种"庞氏结构"维持了铁路股的高分红假象，吸引更多投资者入场，推动泡沫持续膨胀直到1847年彻底破裂。</span>
                            <span class="en"><strong>Hudson paid old shareholders with new investors' money.</strong> He classified capital expenditure as operating costs, hiding losses through fund transfers between affiliated companies. This "Ponzi structure" maintained the illusion of high dividends, attracting more investors until the total collapse of 1847.</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="branch-alt">
