                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800"><span class="zh">"赫德森们"的资本狂飙</span><span class="en">The Capital Frenzy of "The Hudsons"</span></h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1 text-sm"><span class="zh">1845年赫德森推动272项铁路法案，资本承诺约1.32亿英镑——接近英国财政收入的一半。2026年四大云厂商一年资本支出合计7250亿美元——超过英法日三国年度财政支出。这不是预算，这是信仰。</span><span class="en">In 1845 Hudson pushed 272 railway bills with ~£132M commitments — nearly half of British fiscal revenue. In 2026 the Big Four's CapEx totals $725B — exceeding UK, France, Japan combined. This isn't a budget; it's faith.</span></p>
                </div>
