                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800"><span class="zh">"用新股付旧息"的结构</span><span class="en">The "Pay Old Interest with New Shares" Structure</span></h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1 text-sm"><span class="zh">赫德森用新股东的钱付老股东的股息。2026年版：数百亿资金从科技巨头注入AI初创→AI初创向巨头采购云服务→收入流回巨头报表。循环融资放大叙事，虚增估值。全球头部AI企业累计投入约1.4万亿美元，总营收仅6130亿，其中近4800亿被英伟达收入囊中。</span><span class="en">Hudson paid old shareholders with new investors' money. 2026 version: billions flow from tech giants to AI startups → startups buy cloud from giants → revenue flows back. Circular financing amplifies narratives. Global AI companies invested ~$1.4T, but revenue is only $613B, with ~$480B going to NVIDIA.</span></p>
