                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1 text-sm"><span class="zh">1846年崩盘后大量铁路线路客货运量远低于预期。2026年国内智算中心GPU平均利用率不足30%。据中国信通院数据，每投入100元建算力约70元在空转。部分智算中心上架率不足50%。</span><span class="en">After the 1846 crash, many railways had traffic far below expectations. In 2026, GPU utilization averages below 30%. Per CAICT data, for every ¥100 invested in compute, about ¥70 is idling.</span></p>
