                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800"><span class="zh">"技术是真实的，回报是不确定的"</span><span class="en">"The Technology Is Real, Returns Are Uncertain"</span></h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1 text-sm"><span class="zh">1845年的铁路确实是最伟大的基础设施革命之一，但投资者平均回报是负的。2026年的AI确实是最伟大的技术革命之一，但短期回报同样充满不确定性。长江证券："AI正从'技术可行性交易'转向'经济可行性交易'——以前关心'能不能做'，现在关心'能不能赚钱'。"</span><span class="en">Railways in 1845 were indeed one of the greatest infrastructure revolutions, but average investor returns were negative. AI in 2026 is indeed the greatest tech revolution, but short-term returns are equally uncertain. Changjiang Securities: "AI is shifting from 'technical feasibility' to 'economic viability' — from 'can you build it' to 'can you profit from it.'"</span></p>
