        <div class="quote-box mt-6">
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-700 serif"><span class="zh">最重要的区别</span><span class="en">The Most Important Difference</span></p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2"><span class="zh">1845年的瓶颈是铁轨和劳动力——线性约束，可通过时间和资本解决。2026年的瓶颈是电力和变压器——物理约束，扩容周期3-8年，而芯片三个月迭代一代。金融世界与物理世界的时间尺度正在剧烈错位。</span><span class="en">The 1845 bottleneck was rails and labor — linear constraints solvable with time and capital. The 2026 bottleneck is electricity and transformers — physical constraints with 3-8 year expansion cycles, while chips iterate every three months. The time scale of finance and physics are dramatically misaligned.</span></p>
